        "timestamp": "2019-03-14 20:23:57.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nThe additional parameters I see on your config is dmaapContentType and dmaapProtocol. These could be set a generic DFC property separte for MR and DR (as all MR and DR connection will use same contenttype/protocol for a deployment in ONAP). These parameters can be statically setup, however rest of the configuration (like hostname/url/port) will be dynamic/provided by the DCAE platform during deployment (once integration with dmaap BC is in place)",
